# Qoder Auto-Login - Account Template
# Format: email:password (one per line)
# Lines starting with # are ignored
# Blank lines are ignored
#
# Copy this file to accounts.txt and fill in your accounts:
#   cp accounts.txt.example accounts.txt
#
# Example:
# john.doe@gmail.com:MyPassword123
# jane.smith@gmail.com:AnotherPassword456
